These Customer Terms of Service ("Customer Terms") outline your rights and obligations when using DronaHQ's developer tools and platform ("Services"). These terms also apply if you purchase additional expert services provided by DronaHQ to assist in implementing, accelerating, or optimizing your use of the Services ("Expert Services"). Please review these terms carefully. If you are a Customer, these Customer Terms govern your use of the Services and any associated Expert Services. For individual users invited by a Customer, the User Terms of Service will apply.  



##  The Contract  

#### Formation of a Binding Contract  
These Customer Terms, along with any applicable Order Form(s), constitute a legally binding agreement ("Contract") between the Customer and DronaHQ. If specific terms apply (e.g., government-specific provisions), those are incorporated by reference. "We," "our," and "us" refer to the DronaHQ entity specified in the section "Which DronaHQ Entity is Customer Contracting With?"  

#### Agreement on Behalf of Customer  
By purchasing subscriptions, inviting users, using the Services, or continuing usage after updates to these terms, you acknowledge and agree to the Contract on behalf of your organization or entity ("Customer"). Ensure you possess the authority to represent the Customer before proceeding.  

