## Subscriptions and Ordering  

#### Subscription Procurement  
Subscriptions grant Customers and Authorized Users access to the Services for building and using Custom Apps. Subscriptions are tied to individual users and can be purchased through the Services interface or via an Order Form. Subscriptions commence upon activation and are valid for the term specified in the Order Form or Subscription Page.  

#### Adding Users  
Additional users can be added during an active subscription term, with all subscriptions terminating simultaneously unless stated otherwise.  

#### Beta Products  
DronaHQ occasionally offers beta features ("Beta Products") for testing purposes. Beta Products are provided "as is," without warranties or commitments applicable to other Services. Customer feedback on Beta Products is encouraged to refine them for broader release.  

